                    .Col768-1-2.pricing-inclusionsCol.spTop-0
                        h4.u-upper
                            strong Inclusions &amp; Amenities
                        p Our packages include everything you need to make your event a memorable one!
                        ul.features-list
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] #[strong Perfect location] at the Point of the Mountain with easy access to the I-15 freeway.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] #[strong Gorgeous views] of Utah Valley, including surrounding Mount Timpanogos and Utah Lake.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] #[strong Natural stone and wood] throughout.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] #[strong Outdoor patio] with breath-taking views.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] #[strong Beautiful indoor fireplace] with seating area, along with two outdoor fireplaces on the patio.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] #[strong Warming kitchen / caterer's area] with a serving window that opens to The Grand Room.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] #[strong The Grand Room] offers a large, versatile dance / karaoke / entertainment staging area.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] #[strong The Board Room] provides a great space away from the main event for whatever you need. It's a great room for entertaining kids (or adults).
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] #[strong Convenient parking] with extra parking available to the North for larger gatherings.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] #[strong 12 round tables] (60 inch rounds) for seating, #[strong 4 rectangular tables] (6 feet long) for serving, and #[strong 4 bar-height tables] (32 inch bar heights).
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] Elegant, base #[strong table coverings] included at no charge. #[a(href="http://www.renteventutah.com/category/table-cloths" title="View color options for table coverings") View color samples for table coverings online], or at The Lodge.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] 100 White vinyl #[strong folding chairs] also included at no charge.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] #[strong Edison string lights] are available at no extra charge.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] An #[strong event manager] can help plan your event, help with room arrangement, and will be on call during your event.
                    .Col768-1-2.pricing-inclusionsCol.spTop-0
                        h4.u-upper #[strong The Grand Room]
                        p The Grand Room at The Lodge is perfect for any event: weddings, receptions, parties, luncheons, seminars, business meetings, retreats, or family get togethers.
                        ul.features-list
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] 2,200 square feet with flexible seating layouts.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] Large 42" flat screen TV.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] Built in audio / video system.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] Welcome / greeting area with room for gifts.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] One indoor, two outdoor fireplaces.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] Outdoor patio with amazing views of Utah valley.
                        h4.u-upper.sp-top--2x #[strong Bride's Room]
                        p Bride's can now enjoy one of our favorite additions. The Bride's Room is the perfect, cozy space for the Bride to get ready for her special day.
                        ul.features-list
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] Comfortable vanity where Bride can get pampered.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] Large head-to-toe mirror.
                            li #[span.fa.fa-check-square] Two large windows to bring in the natural light.
                        h4.u-upper.sp-top--2x #[strong The Board Room]
